    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"515757\">@Luke Boswell</span> , I can wait, no problem. Let me know if I can be of any help.</p>",
        "id": 583167410,
        "sender_full_name": "Aurélien Geron",
        "timestamp": 1775094944
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>We have the \"echo\" platform up and running now which is designed for examples... if your interested someone needs to start tinkering with that and thinking about the exercism track again.</p>",
        "id": 583167753,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1775095212
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You can hit bugs with more complex apps ... but it should be pretty stable for simple things I think</p>",
        "id": 583167808,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1775095242
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>$ cat test/echo/hello.roc\nmain! = |_args| {\n    echo!(&quot;Hello, World!&quot;)\n    Ok({})\n}\n$ roc test/echo/hello.roc\nHello, World!\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 583168153,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1775095448
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It has a single effect that is imported by default <code>echo! : Str =&gt; {}</code></p>",
        "id": 583168363,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1775095596
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and main is</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>main! : List(Str) =&gt; Try({}, [Exit(I8), ..])\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 583168457,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1775095667
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks. I'm surprised there's no need for an <code>app</code> section, and no <code>import pf.echo!</code>. Is echo the default platform?</p>",
        "id": 583171042,
        "sender_full_name": "Aurélien Geron",
        "timestamp": 1775097482
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yeah, it's a default platform that is always available for the purpose of tutorials and teaching Roc</p>",
        "id": 583171130,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1775097577
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The idea of not having the <code>app</code> header or import statements, is that we can introduce those concepts later when onboarding people.</p>",
        "id": 583171210,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1775097638
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Cool, I like it!</p>",
